        <section id="about" class="about section" aria-labelledby="about-title">

            <div class="container">

                <h2 id="about-title" class="section-title" data-en="About Me" data-tr="Hakkımda">
                    About Me
                </h2>

                <div class="about-content">
                    <p data-en="I am a Software Engineering student and active intern focused on backend development and iOS applications. I work with REST APIs, MVC-based applications, databases and mobile app architecture."
                       data-tr="Backend geliştirme ve iOS uygulamaları üzerine odaklanan bir Yazılım Mühendisliği öğrencisi ve aktif stajyerim. REST API, MVC tabanlı uygulamalar, veritabanları ve mobil uygulama mimarisi üzerinde çalışıyorum.">
                        I am a Software Engineering student and active intern focused on backend development and iOS applications. I work with REST APIs, MVC-based applications, databases and mobile app architecture.
                    </p>

                    <p data-en="My experience includes Laravel/PHP backend development, C#/.NET banking workflows, Oracle database operations and Swift-based iOS applications using UIKit, SwiftUI and MVVM."
                       data-tr="Deneyimim Laravel/PHP backend geliştirme, C#/.NET ile bankacılık iş akışları, Oracle veritabanı işlemleri ve UIKit, SwiftUI, MVVM kullanan Swift tabanlı iOS uygulamalarını kapsıyor.">
                        My experience includes Laravel/PHP backend development, C#/.NET banking workflows, Oracle database operations and Swift-based iOS applications using UIKit, SwiftUI and MVVM.
                    </p>

                    <p data-en="I focus on writing clean, maintainable code and building practical software that connects backend logic, data management and user-facing applications."
                       data-tr="Temiz, sürdürülebilir kod yazmaya; backend mantığını, veri yönetimini ve kullanıcıya dönük uygulamaları bir araya getiren pratik yazılımlar geliştirmeye odaklanıyorum.">
                        I focus on writing clean, maintainable code and building practical software that connects backend logic, data management and user-facing applications.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

