                <p class="contact-intro"
                   data-en="I am currently open to software engineering internships and junior backend/mobile developer opportunities."
                   data-tr="Yazılım mühendisliği stajı ve junior backend/mobil geliştirici fırsatlarına açığım.">
                    I am currently open to software engineering internships and junior backend/mobile developer opportunities.
                </p>

                <div class="contact-wrapper">

                    <aside class="contact-info-card" aria-label="Contact information">

                        <div class="contact-info-list">

                            <a class="contact-info-item" href="mailto:aysenurkendirciss@gmail.com">
